ZH: 几乎每天早上我都喝咖啡。
EN: I drink coffee almost every morning.

ZH: 这部电影几乎没有人看过。
EN: Almost no one has watched this movie.

ZH: 几乎所有的孩子都喜欢吃冰淇淋。
EN: Almost all children like to eat ice cream.

ZH: 她几乎一整天都在工作。
EN: She works almost all day long.

ZH: 这家餐馆的菜几乎都很好吃。
EN: The dishes in this restaurant are almost all delicious.

ZH: 几乎没有什么事情比在家休息更舒服。
EN: There is almost nothing more comfortable than resting at home.

ZH: 那个学生几乎从不迟到。
EN: That student is almost never late.

ZH: 几乎所有人都参加了公司的年度派对。
EN: Almost everyone attended the company's annual party.

ZH: 这个项目几乎完成了。
EN: The project is almost complete.

ZH: 我家离学校几乎只有五分钟的路程。
EN: My house is only about five minutes away from the school.

ZH: 他的论文几乎写完了。
EN: His thesis is almost finished.

ZH: 她几乎每周都去健身房锻炼。
EN: She goes to the gym to exercise almost every week.

ZH: 冬天的时候，这里几乎没有人。
EN: There are almost no people here in winter.

ZH: 这座城市的景点几乎都被游客占领了。
EN: Almost all of the city's attractions have been taken over by tourists.

ZH: 他几乎每天晚上都加班工作。
EN: He works overtime almost every night.

ZH: 风景区里的树几乎都已经换上了金黄色。
EN: The trees in the scenic area have almost all turned golden.

ZH: 这个问题几乎所有人都很困惑。
EN: Almost everyone is puzzled by this problem.

ZH: 全家几乎每周都一起吃早饭。
EN: The whole family almost eats breakfast together every week.

ZH: 这里的气温几乎每天都在零下。
EN: The temperature here is almost below zero every day.

ZH: 几乎每个城市都有自己的地标建筑。
EN: Almost every city has its own landmark building.
